clinical_study.brief_title: Phase I/II Clinical Trial of Recombinant Novel Coronavirus (COVID-19) Vaccine (Adenovirus Type 5 Vector) for Inhalation
clinical_study.official_title: A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-Controlled Phase I/II Clinical Trial to Evaluate the Safety and Immunogenicity of Ad5-nCoV for Inhalation in Adults 18 Years of Age and Older

collaborator.agency: Jiangsu Province Centers for Disease Control and Prevention

brief_summary.textblock: This study is a randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled I/II clinical trial, in order to evaluate the safety and immunogenicity of Recombinant Novel Coronavirus Vaccine (Adenovirus Type 5 Vector) for Inhalation in adults 18 years of Age and Older.

study_design_info.masking: Quadruple (Participant, Care Provider, Investigator, Outcomes Assessor)

primary_outcome.description: The occurrence of Adverse Reactions (AR) in all groups.

primary_outcome.time_frame: Within the first and final vaccination up until 12 months after the final vaccination
primary_outcome.description: The occurrence of Serious Adverse Events (SAE) in all groups.

secondary_outcome.description: The occurance of Adverse Events/Reactions (AE/AR) in all groups.
The occurance of Adverse Events/Reactions (AE/AR) in all groups.
Changes in laboratory test indicators (including white blood cell count, lymphocyte count, etc), and respiratory rate in all groups.

secondary_outcome.measure: GMT, seroconversion rate and GMI of Covid-19 S protein RBD specific antibody
secondary_outcome.time_frame: Before the first dose, 28 days after first dose, before the second dose, 14 days after the second dose
secondary_outcome.description: GMT, seroconversion rate and GMI of S protein RBD specific antibody by ELISA in all groups.

secondary_outcome.measure: GMT, seroconversion rate, GMI of neutralizing antibody (pseudovirus) against Covid-19
secondary_outcome.time_frame: Before the first dose, 28 days after the first dose, bofore the second dose, 14 days after the second dose
secondary_outcome.description: GMT, seroconversion rate, GMI of neutralizing antibody (pseudovirus) against Covid-19 in all groups.

secondary_outcome.measure: GMT and seroconversion rate of neutralizing antibody against Covid-19
secondary_outcome.description: GMT and seroconversion rate of neutralizing antibody against Covid-19 in all goups.

secondary_outcome.time_frame: Before the first dose, 14 days after the first dose
secondary_outcome.description: The positive rate of IFN-γ、TNF-α、IL-5、IL-4、IL-13 by stimulated by S protein ELISpot in all groups.
